column4: This game actually makes it fun to learn, damn if only the American school system knew how to do that.  10/10 learned more from this game than my science class.

Early Access Game Review: Even getting lost in space is fun  This is a great simulation game and at this stage the UI is already very poslished and main functions like causing interplanetary collision and making fun by adjusting physics of a planet/star is intuitive and easy.   What I'd like to require as a fun function is a spacecraft that we can travel across the space!  It's a cool ride already!
